data.description: Country living close to town in this 3 bedroom/2 1/2 bath ranch home. Tons of potential in this hidden gem. Large lot with mature trees and many fruit trees. Large shop and an additional outbuilding currently used for boat storage. Home features beautiful hardwood floors, main floor laundry, dining area with sliding doors to covered deck. Unfinished basement with full bath and egress window ready to finish your way. Fresh paint. New hot water heater, water softner and sump pump. Furnace well maintained and serviced. Wired for a whole house generator.
